A GILDED EXOTICS COLLECTION

Inspired By: Stellar Times, Louis Vuitton

  • Top Notes: White Amber

  • Middle Notes: Peru Balm

  • Base Notes: Orange Blossom

Looks like stardust, but acts like trouble.

White amber floats in first—soft, warm, and suspiciously innocent. Then comes Peru balm, all golden glow and slow-burn seduction. Just when you’re lulled into a cosmic daydream, orange blossom crashes the party with a fresh, flirty kick.

It’s lightyears from tame. Sweet, lingers, bold, and just the right amount of scandal in space.

Mood: Radiant. Warm. Elegant.
